application_type_description.arbitrary: Arbitrary application is a type of application that can do anything. This, however, means that application's configuration (if present) is dynamic, which means that you will not be able to edit other than in raw JSON.
application_type_description.host: Host application doesn't do anything by itself. Rather, it serves as an "adapter" of sorts between third-party applications or scripts and Telephonist API.
application_type_description.custom: Custom application is the same as arbitrary, the only difference is that you can set you own application type.

host_application_alerts: This application is of type "host". Use the settings below to configure the host's behaviour.
